title: Phish 7_21_13
description:
Sunday, 07/21/2013 

FirstMerit Bank Pavilion at Northerly Island, Chicago, IL

Set 1: Dinner and a Movie, AC/DC Bag > Maze, Mound, Funky Bitch > Bathtub Gin, Wilson, Water in the Sky, Boogie On Reggae Woman > Run Like an Antelope[1]

Set 2: Energy > Ghost[2] -> The Lizards, Harpua[3], Run Like an Antelope

Encore: Character Zero

[1] Aborted.
[2] Seven Below teases from Fish and Mike.
[3] With the cast of Second City.

Notes: The first set's Antelope was aborted and the band had to leave the stage due to a heavy rain storm. Ghost contained Seven Below teases from Fish and Mike. Harpua contained an appearance by the cast of Second City and a narration by Mike.
